  "detailed_description": "<u><strong>Gameplay</strong></u><br><br>Welcome to the ultimate cooperative virtual reality experience! In this game, you and your friends will embark on a mysterious and thrilling adventure that will test your skills and courage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ddcb438556c5d9203badb2bf71122ed6.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ddcb438556c5d9203badb2bf71122ed6.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ddcb438556c5d9203badb2bf71122ed6.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To survive in this strange and ominous world, you'll need to work together, using a combination of guns with realistic mechanisms and melee weapons to take down your enemies and make your way through the ever-changing maze. With each kill, you’ll grow stronger and will be able to purchase upgrades with the coins collected from the corpses of your enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/bdb682d9759af19b389fa724ec412951.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/bdb682d9759af19b389fa724ec412951.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/bdb682d9759af19b389fa724ec412951.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With each new level comes a new theme, from dark and haunted Ruins with storms to a vintage American diner or a bowling alley. And because the maze is randomly generated, no two playthroughs will ever be the same.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/4a3e3ef899a1112d1c078319112cc697.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/4a3e3ef899a1112d1c078319112cc697.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/4a3e3ef899a1112d1c078319112cc697.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/c794e4329d4e1e7075492873c00c6808.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/c794e4329d4e1e7075492873c00c6808.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/c794e4329d4e1e7075492873c00c6808.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But be warned: this is not a game for the faint of heart. With its unsettling atmosphere and spine-tingling soundtrack, you'll be constantly on edge, never sure what lurks around the next corner.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ff1b4ffa1ec7aceec645e728cdc8ac6d.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ff1b4ffa1ec7aceec645e728cdc8ac6d.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ff1b4ffa1ec7aceec645e728cdc8ac6d.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/1aead0b5d5ab365d2443330b96780c66.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/1aead0b5d5ab365d2443330b96780c66.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/1aead0b5d5ab365d2443330b96780c66.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>Lore</strong></u><br><br>The Maze is a VR Co-op game in which human players arrive in a new realm after being teleported from their homelands. The size and purpose of the maze is unknown, the only thing that is certain is that they have to survive in this extremely harsh environment.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/fd3cbb525854db7f51f533f3c8256141.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/fd3cbb525854db7f51f533f3c8256141.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/fd3cbb525854db7f51f533f3c8256141.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The Maze changes according to our memories, imagination, dreams, and transforms itself into an even more chaotic realm as more people arrive. Environments change according to the memories of the living beings within it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/32e0ba8c832b5b9e54629aaa760883c1.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/32e0ba8c832b5b9e54629aaa760883c1.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/32e0ba8c832b5b9e54629aaa760883c1.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>_____________________________________________________________________________<br><br><br><br><br><strong>So gather your friends, strap on your VR headset, and get ready for the adventure of a lifetime. Do you have what it takes to survive the maze?</strong><br><br><br><br>_____________________________________________________________________________",
  "about_the_game": "<u><strong>Gameplay</strong></u><br><br>Welcome to the ultimate cooperative virtual reality experience! In this game, you and your friends will embark on a mysterious and thrilling adventure that will test your skills and courage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ddcb438556c5d9203badb2bf71122ed6.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ddcb438556c5d9203badb2bf71122ed6.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ddcb438556c5d9203badb2bf71122ed6.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To survive in this strange and ominous world, you'll need to work together, using a combination of guns with realistic mechanisms and melee weapons to take down your enemies and make your way through the ever-changing maze. With each kill, you’ll grow stronger and will be able to purchase upgrades with the coins collected from the corpses of your enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/bdb682d9759af19b389fa724ec412951.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/bdb682d9759af19b389fa724ec412951.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/bdb682d9759af19b389fa724ec412951.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With each new level comes a new theme, from dark and haunted Ruins with storms to a vintage American diner or a bowling alley. And because the maze is randomly generated, no two playthroughs will ever be the same.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/4a3e3ef899a1112d1c078319112cc697.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/4a3e3ef899a1112d1c078319112cc697.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/4a3e3ef899a1112d1c078319112cc697.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/c794e4329d4e1e7075492873c00c6808.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/c794e4329d4e1e7075492873c00c6808.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/c794e4329d4e1e7075492873c00c6808.mp4?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But be warned: this is not a game for the faint of heart. With its unsettling atmosphere and spine-tingling soundtrack, you'll be constantly on edge, never sure what lurks around the next corner.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ff1b4ffa1ec7aceec645e728cdc8ac6d.poster.avif?t=1753274617\" width=350 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1339110/extras/ff1b4ffa1ec7aceec645e728cdc8ac6d.webm?t=1753274617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://share